{
  "chapter": "102",
  "title": "张释之冯唐列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "张释之初入仕途",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>，是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">堵阳</span>人，字季。有<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">兄</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张仲\">仲（张仲）</span>同居。凭家财做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">骑郎</span>，侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孝文帝</span>，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>没得升迁，无所知名。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>说：\"做官久了减损<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张仲\">仲（张仲）</span>的家产，不顺遂。\" 想自辞回乡。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中郎将</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>知他贤能，舍不得他走，于是请求调<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>补任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>朝见完毕，于是上前陈说便利之事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说：\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：卑之毋甚高论\">卑之，毋甚高论（卑之毋甚高论）</span>，说些当今可以施行的。\" 于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>谈论<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>之间的事情，讲<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所以丧失、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>所以兴起的缘由良久。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>称好，于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">谒者仆射</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "虎圈谏言",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>跟从皇上出行，登上<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">虎圈</span>。皇上问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上林尉</span>有关<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">禽兽</span>的簿册，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀</span>问，尉左顾右盼，都答不上来。<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">虎圈</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">啬夫</span>从旁代尉对答皇上所问<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">禽兽</span>簿册甚为详尽，想显示自己口若悬河应答无穷的本事。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说：\"当官的不当这样吗？尉无用！\" 于是下诏<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">啬夫</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">上林令</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>迟了一会儿上前说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>觉得<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周勃</span>是什么人？\" 皇上说：\"是长者。\" 又问：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东阳侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张相如</span>又是什么人？\" 皇上又说：\"是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">绛侯</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">东阳侯</span>号称长者，这<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">两人</span>议事时都说不出口，难道学这<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">啬夫</span>喋喋不休伶牙俐齿吗！况且<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝因任用刀笔之吏，官吏争以急迫苛察相竞，然而他们的弊端只是虚文形式罢了，没有恻隐之实。因此不闻其过，一路衰败至<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">二世</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>土崩瓦解。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>因<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">啬夫</span>的口辩而越级提升他，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>恐怕<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>会随风效仿，争为口辩而无其实。况且下面效仿上面比影响影响还快，举措不可不慎。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说：\"好。\" 于是不再<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">啬夫</span>。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "问秦之敝",
      "text": "皇上登上<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">车</span>，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">参乘</span>，慢行，问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>的弊政。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>都据实回答。到宫中，皇上<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">公车令</span>。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "劾太子不敬",
      "text": "不久，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span>共乘<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">车</span>入朝，不在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">司马门</span>下车，于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>追上去阻止<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span>不得入殿门。并以不下公门不敬罪弹劾，上奏。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>听说，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>摘下帽子谢罪说：\"教儿<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>不严谨。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">薄太后</span>便派使者承诏<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁王</span>，然后才得入。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>因此看重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中大夫</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "霸陵谏厚葬",
      "text": "不久，升至<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中郎将</span>。跟从出行到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">霸陵</span>，居高俯临。当时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">慎夫人</span>随行，皇上指示<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">慎夫人</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">新丰</span>之路,说：\"这是通往<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">邯郸</span>的路。\" 让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">慎夫人</span>鼓<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">瑟</span>，皇上亲自倚<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">瑟</span>而歌，情意凄惨悲怀，回头对<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>说：\"啊！用<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北山</span>之石做<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">椁</span>，用苎麻絮填塞，用漆粘合缝隙，难道能动得了吗！\" 左右都说：\"好。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>上前说：\"若其中有可让人贪图之物，即使铸固<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南山</span>也会有缝隙；若其中无可贪图之物，即使没有石<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">椁</span>，又何忧虑呢！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>称好。其后<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "惊马案",
      "text": "不久，皇上出行到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中渭桥</span>，有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span>从桥下走出，拉<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘舆</span>的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>受惊。于是派骑兵抓住他，交<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>处理。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>审问。回答说：\"本县人，听到清道回避，躲在桥下。久了，以为皇上已过，便出来，看见<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">乘舆</span>车骑，便跑开了。\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>奏议，认为<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">一人</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">犯跸</span>，应罚金。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>怒道：\"此人亲惊我<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，我<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>赖柔和，若是别的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，岂不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">摔</span>伤我吗？而<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>却判他罚金！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>说：\"法是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>与<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>共同遵守的。如今法律如此而要加重，是法不能取信于<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>。当时，皇上若让人立刻<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>他也就罢了。既然已交<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>是<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的公平，一旦倾斜则<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>用法轻重不一，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>将怎样安置他们的手足？望<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>明察。\" 良久，皇上说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>判得对。\""
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "盗环案",
      "text": "此后有人偷<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">高庙</span>座前的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玉环</span>，被抓获，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>大怒，交<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>审理。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>依律盗<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>服御物者议罪，奏请<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">弃市</span>。皇上大怒说：\"此人不讲道义，竟偷<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">先帝</span>庙器，我把他交<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>，想将他处<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族诛</span>，而<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>却以法奏此刑，不是我共同承奉<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>的心意。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>摘冠顿首谢罪说：\"依法判罪这已够了。况且罪等，但要按逆顺之理排差等。如今盗<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">宗庙</span>器就灭<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">族</span>，万一再有愚<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长陵</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>一把土，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>将何以加罪？\" 良久，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>与<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太后</span>商议后，才同意<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>的判决。当时，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">条侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">周亚夫</span>与<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">梁相</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">山都侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恬开</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>议事公平，便结为亲密朋友。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>由此为<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>所称赞。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "景帝时期",
      "text": "后来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>驾崩，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>即位，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>恐惧，称病。想辞职离去，怕大祸临头；想去请罪，又不知结果如何。用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王生</span>的计策，终于见皇帝谢罪，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>未加责怪。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "王生结穇事",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王生</span>，善讲<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">黄老</span>之言，是处<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。曾被召到朝廷中，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三公九卿</span>尽会集而立，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王生</span>是老人，说\"我袜带松了\"，回头对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>说：\"给我结袜带！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>跪下替他结上。结完后，有人对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王生</span>说：\"为何偏要在朝廷上侮辱<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>，让他跪着结袜带？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王生</span>说：\"我老而且贱，自料终究对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>没什么帮助。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>是如今<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天下</span>的名<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，我故意羞辱<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">廷尉</span>，让他跪结袜带，想借此抬高他。\" 诸公听到后，都赞许<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王生</span>而更尊重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "晚年与后代",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张廷尉</span>侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span><span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>，出任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">淮南王相</span>，仍是因先前的过失。久之，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">释之（张释之）</span>去世。他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儿子</span>叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张挚</span>，字长公，官至<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">大夫</span>，后免职。因不能<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">取</span>悦当世，所以终身不做官。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "冯唐出身",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯唐</span>，他的祖<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>是<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>人。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>迁徙到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>兴起后迁到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">安陵</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>以孝著称，任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中郎署长</span>，侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "论将才",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>乘辇经过，问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>：\"父老何以还在做郎官？家住哪里？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>都据实回答。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>说：\"我住<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">代</span>的时候，我的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">尚食监</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">高袪</span>多次对我说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李齐</span>的贤能，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜鹿</span>下<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">作战</span>的事。如今我每次吃饭，心中未尝不想着<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">钜鹿</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>老知道他吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>回答说：\"尚不如<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>的为将之才。\" 皇上说：\"为什么？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的祖<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>时，做<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">官将</span>，与<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>交好。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>亲做过<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">代相</span>，与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李齐</span>交好，知他的为人。\" 皇上既听闻<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>的为人，很高兴，拍大腿说：\"唉！我独不能得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>之时的人做我的将领，我岂忧虑<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>哉！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>说：\"唉主<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>！<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>即使得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>，也不能用他们。\" 皇上大怒，起身入宫内。良久，召<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>责备说：\"您为何当众羞辱我，难道没有单独的场合吗？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>谢罪说：\"鄙人不知忌讳。\""
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "论用将之道",
      "text": "当时，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>新近大举入侵朝那，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span><span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">北地都尉</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">卬</span>。皇上以胡寇为忧，最终又问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>：\"您怎么知道我不能用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>？\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>回答说：\"<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>听说上古君王派将时，跪下推着车轮说，城门以内的事，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">寡人</span>决断；城门以外的事，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span>决断。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">军功爵赏</span>都由外决定，回来再奏报。这并非虚言。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>的祖<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">父</span>说，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>做<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>将戍边，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">军市</span>的税收都自用来犒赏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，赏赐由外决定，不受朝廷干扰。委任他责成事功，所以<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>能尽其智能，挑选<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千三百乘</span>，弓骑<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万三千</span>，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">百金</span>之<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span><span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十万</span>，因此北逐<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">单于</span>，<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击破</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">东胡</span>，灭<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">澹林</span>，西抑强<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>，南御<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">韩</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">魏</span>。那时，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">赵</span>几乎称霸。此后碰上<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">赵王迁</span>即位，他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">母</span>亲是娼女出身。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王迁</span>即位，就听信<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">郭开</span>谗言，终<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>，让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颜聚</span>代他。所以兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">败</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒北逃，被<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>所擒灭。如今<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>私下听说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏尚</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中守</span>，他的<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">军市</span>税收全用来犒赏<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒，私人养钱，<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">五天（时长）</span>一杀<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">牛</span>，犒飨宾客、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">军吏</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">舍人</span>，因此<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>远避，不近<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">云中</span>之塞。敌虏曾一次入侵，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：魏尚\">尚（魏尚）</span>率车骑<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻击</span>，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死其众。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒都是平民<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人子</span>，从田中投军，怎么懂<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">尺籍伍符</span>？<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">整天（时长）</span>力<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">战</span>，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">斩首</span>俘虏，上报功劳到幕府，一句话不相应，文吏就以法处置。该给的赏赐不兑现而吏据法必究。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>愚昧，以为<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>法太明，赏太轻，罚太重。况且<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中守</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏尚</span>因上报功劳首虏差六级，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>就下交狱吏，削他的爵位，罚他做苦工。由此说来，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">陛下</span>即使得到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">廉颇</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李牧</span>，也不能用。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>确实愚昧，触犯忌讳，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死罪</span><span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">死罪</span>！\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文帝</span>高兴。这一天令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯唐</span>持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">节</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">赦免</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏尚</span>，再任他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">云中守</span>，而<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">任命</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">车骑都尉</span>，主管<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">中尉</span>及郡国的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "晚年与后代",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">七年</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">景帝</span>即位，任<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">楚相</span>，后被免职。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">武帝</span>即位，访求<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">贤良</span>，举荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯唐</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>当时年九十余，不能再做官，就用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">唐（冯唐）</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">儿子</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">冯遂</span>为郎官。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯遂\">遂（冯遂）</span>字<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯遂\">王孙（冯遂）</span>，也是奇<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>，与我交好。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">张季（张释之）</span>论<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">长者</span>，守法不阿意；<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">冯公（冯唐）</span>论将领，意味深长啊！意味深长啊！俗话说\"不知其人，视其友\"。<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二</span><span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">君</span>的言论所称赞者，可铭于<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">廊庙</span>。书上说\"<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">不偏不党</span>，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>荡荡；不党不偏，<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">王道</span>便便\"。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">张季（张释之）</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">冯公（冯唐）</span>差不多了。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张释之\">张季（张释之）</span>未遇时，得<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">袁盎</span>赏识。 <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">太子</span>惧法，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">啬夫</span>无状。 惊<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>罚金之判，盗<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">环</span>之议醒悟君上。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：冯唐\">冯公（冯唐）</span>白首，论将意味深长。 因对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">李齐</span>，终为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">魏尚</span>收功。"
    }
  }
}